ii) resembles a larger or denser ice giant on\na currently eccentric orbit. Distinguishing these three possibilities strongly\nmotivates follow-up observations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 Dec 2019 19:00:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 30 Jan 2020 11:12:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-12"}
